# Content Concierge (PoC1)

PoC1 bootstrap for a modular Content Concierge service using FastAPI.

## Run locally

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -e .
uvicorn api.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

# PODSTMAN:
get session 
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/insights -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"user_id\":\"cust_001\"}"

session Q&A 
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/sessions/<SESSION_ID>/ask -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"question\":\"How does AAPL relate to my portfolio?\",\"conversation\":[]}"
